2082.subject: ASAP
2082.descrlong: Provides supplemental reading comprehension support for students needing assistance with reading strategies in upper division writing courses.  Workshop topics range from practice in reading comprehension, and reading rate to negotiating academic text.  Students work with a tutor from the Academic Skills Achievement Program (ASAP).  Groups meet one hour per week. Credit/no credit only.
